data.text: @MadAboutMeghan Well said! I agree with you 100%. The power of love will prevail!  It's time to boycott trash news, put them out of business!

@MadAboutMeghan The haters need to find a life....Jealousy is a nasty trait in some humans.  Leave
Prince Harry and Meghan to sort out their own life!
@MadAboutMeghan This E! News story is just garbage because there is nothing in it. They’re rather looking for bad story on Meghan.
@LuluInThePalace @MadAboutMeghan The first thing I thought is no real friend would be talking to the press - I hope many think that as well in considering the source

@LuluInThePalace @MadAboutMeghan So true! It was so nice to see Harry have someone by his side at last week’s royal walkabout. The now royal quartet can do a lot of good things if everyone will calm down and let them.
@guinevere530 @MadAboutMeghan I certainly hope so. I’m so excited about both! I can barely handle it!!

@LuluInThePalace @MadAboutMeghan Hopefully it will calm down.. and in a way Kate’s baby will take some of the pressure off. The press will be somewhat distracted, so maybe she can get some peace before the wedding.
@guinevere530 @MadAboutMeghan She’s a strong girl & her mum is as well. They’ll be ok. But it’s a real shame & an act of betrayal.

@LuluInThePalace @MadAboutMeghan And it didn’t take long..all the so called friends and family looking to cash in. The tabloids are going to be relentless..already today they are calling her the new Fergie..and I don’t think it’s in a complimentary way..sad.

@MadAboutMeghan I have a friend who’s know MM’s mum for over 35yrs. While she’s shared stories/photos w/me privately, she would never go public. She told me what bits of info I could/couldn’t share w/others. True friends don’t talk to the media w/o consent. It’s a shame this is happening.

@MadAboutMeghan What her so called best friend told the tabloids was a nothing burger! 
There's more crazy in the BRF.
@MadAboutMeghan It was expected. The Royal family did their extensive background check on her and they were satisfied. Whatever her friends and jealous half Sister will say won’t change anything
